<!-- Dosage Table Section -->
<section class=mb-stack-lg>
<div class=bg-white border border-outline-variant rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm>
<div class=p-stack-md bg-surface-container-low border-b border-outline-variant flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-3>
<div>
<h2 class=text-title-lg font-headline-md text-on-surface>Crop-wise Dosage Schedule</h2>
<p class=text-caption text-on-surface-variant>Standardized per-acre recommendations. Search and filter above to refine results.</p>
</div>
<button id=pdf-download-btn class=text-primary text-label-md flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline whitespace-nowrap>
<span class=material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]>download</span> Download PDF Guide
</button>
</div>
<div id=dosage-table-wrap class=overflow-x-auto>
<table class=w-full text-left border-collapse style=min-width:750px>
<thead>
<tr class=bg-surface-container-high border-b border-outline-variant>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>Crop</th>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>Fertilizer</th>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>NPK</th>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>Dosage/Acre</th>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>Timing</th>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>Soil</th>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>Type</th>
<th class=p-4 text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider>Instructions</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody id=dosage-tbody class=divide-y divide-outline-variant></tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class=p-4 bg-error-container/5 border-t border-outline-variant flex items-center gap-3>
<span class=material-symbols-outlined text-error>info</span>
<p class=text-caption text-on-surface-variant font-label-md>Local soil testing at KVK centres is recommended for final calibration.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Crop Recommendation Section -->
<section class=mb-stack-lg>
<div class=bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm>
<div class=p-stack-md bg-surface-container-low border-b border-outline-variant>
<h2 class=text-title-lg font-headline-md text-on-surface>Get Personalized Recommendations</h2>
<p class=text-caption text-on-surface-variant>Select your crop, soil type and preference to get matching fertilizer suggestions.</p>
</div>
<div class=p-stack-md>
<div class=flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 mb-stack-md fert-filter-row id=rec-form>
<select id=rec-crop class=flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary outline-none>
<option value=">Select Crop</option>
<option>Wheat</option><option>Rice</option><option>Cotton</option><option>Sugarcane</option>
<option>Tomato</option><option>Onion</option><option>Soybean</option><option>Groundnut</option>
<option>Maize</option><option>Bajra</option>
</select>
<select id=rec-soil class=flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary outline-none>
<option value=>Select Soil Type</option>
<option>Loamy</option><option>Clay</option><option>Sandy</option><option>Black</option><option>Red</option><option>Alluvial</option>
</select>
<select id=rec-pref class=flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary outline-none>
<option value=>Any Preference</option>
<option value=Chemical>Chemical</option>
<option value=Organic>Organic</option>
</select>
<button id=rec-btn class=px-8 py-3 bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-md rounded-lg active:scale-95 transition-transform whitespace-nowrap>Get Recommendations</button>
</div>
<div id=rec-results class=hidden>
<h3 class=text-label-md font-bold text-on-surface mb-3>Recommended Fertilizers</h3>
<div id=rec-cards class=grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 rec-cards-grid mb-4></div>
<div id=rec-organic-alt class=hidden mt-3 p-4 bg-secondary-container/20 border border-secondary-container rounded-xl>
<p class=text-label-md font-bold text-secondary mb-1>🌿 Organic Alternative</p>
<div id=rec-organic-content></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Soil Health Bento Grid -->
<section class=mb-stack-lg>
<h2 class=text-headline-md font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-stack-md>Core Soil Health Principles</h2>
<div class=grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6>
<div class=md:col-span-2 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6>
<div class=w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container flex items-center justify-center shrink-0>
<span class=material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]>science</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class=text-title-lg font-title-lg text-primary mb-1>Pre-Sowing Soil Testing</h4>
<p class=text-body-md text-on-surface-variant>Measure pH and available nutrients. Farmers save an average of ₹2,500/acre by eliminating unnecessary applications.</p>
<a id=kvk-lab-link class=inline-block mt-2 text-primary font-label-md hover:underline cursor-pointer>Map of nearest KVK Labs →</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class=bg-secondary-container/20 border-2 border-secondary-container p-6 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between>
<h4 class=text-title-lg font-title-lg text-secondary mb-2>Nitrogen Fixation</h4>
<p class=text-caption text-on-surface-variant>Integrating legumes in your rotation can naturally add up to 30-40kg of Nitrogen per hectare.</p>
</div>
<div class=bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm flex flex-col>
<div class=flex items-center gap-3 mb-3>
<span class=material-symbols-outlined text-primary>compost</span>
<h4 class=text-label-md font-bold text-primary>Organic Enrichment</h4>
</div>
<p class=text-caption text-on-surface-variant>Use FYM (Farm Yard Manure) to enhance the Cation Exchange Capacity (CEC) of your soil.</p>
<a id=soil-lab-link class=inline-block mt-3 text-primary text-caption font-label-md hover:underline cursor-pointer>Find Soil Testing Lab near you →</a>
</div>
<div class=md:col-span-2 bg-primary text-on-primary p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center>
<div class=w-full md:w-2/3>
<h4 class=text-title-lg font-title-lg mb-1>Erosion Control & Techniques</h4>
<p class=text-body-md opacity-90>Implement mulching and contour bunding. Preserving topsoil prevents nutrient washout during heavy monsoon rains.</p>
</div>
<div class=w-full md:w-1/3 flex justify-end>
<button id=learn-techniques-btn class=px-6 py-2 bg-white text-primary font-label-md rounded-full shadow-lg>Learn Techniques</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
